<div class="p">Until, commended by Who Ought to Know,</div>
<div class="p">None question he's the ghost of Cicero.</div>
<div class="p">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; He tells of an historic coalition:</div>
<div class="p">How College Brat, unbiased academician,</div>
<div class="p">And less punctilious pedagogue united,</div>
